name: Spaceport City
LocationDStext: If your thief or scout present, Force drain +1 here. May not be deployed to Bespin, Dagobah, Endor, Hoth or Yavin 4.
LocationLStext: If you have a non-unique Rebel leader at same or related site, Force drain +1 here. May not be deployed to Bespin, Dagobah, Endor, Hoth or Yavin 4.
